
********************************************************************************

                   Generic master-field measurement functions

********************************************************************************


Files
-----

farchive.c       I/O functions for real-valued observable fields.

fiodat.c         I/O utility programs for real-valued observable fields.

fldops.c         Basic utility programs for observable fields.

latavg.c         Lattice averages of observable fields.

pt2pt.c          Computation of point-to-point correlation functions.


Include file
------------

The file msfcts.h defines the prototypes for all externally accessible
functions that are defined in the *.c files listed above.
